Class Watcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • buckets.Watcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Subscriber, java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class Watcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements Subscriber, java.io.Serializable
    watches a given collection of directories and notifies the rule manager when files are created.
